{"tid":87820,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"心目中神鵰俠侶最佳選角","createTime":"2017-01-20T06:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T16:33:00.000Z","uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32e6c48e0265099f9bf189e1d884f46d7bdea48a","tid":87820,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"楊過-無心水<br />\n幾個版本都無一個好岩心水 年輕既楊過2014版最似 但16年後唔太岩心水 黃曉明太成熟 做16年後其實幾岩FEEL 而古天樂就年輕時又唔似 16年後又唔夠成熟<br />\n<br />\n小龍女-劉亦菲<br />\n我諗呢個公認啦 太完美 PERFECTLY FIT 其實呢個角色都岩D演技麻麻既演員 好多位都唔洗做表情 李若彤靚係靚 但係總係差少少野咁 可能個樣成熟D 少左個份未見過世面既氣質<br />\n<br />\n郭靖-2014版<br />\n呢個版本最貼近小說 郭靖敦請戇直粗眉大眼 反而2006版太過老 明明楊過青年時 佢都係40歲未到 但06版老到唔似樣 而且唔夠敦厚 又唔夠正氣 如下圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lajiaobagua.com/file/image/2015/0505/14308341036613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lajiaobagua.com%2Ffile%2Fimage%2F2015%2F0505%2F14308341036613.jpg&h=d0f60ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n14年版成個人望落就FIT晒啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.buzzhand.net/uploads/8d/b/454752/1421818491377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.buzzhand.net%2Fuploads%2F8d%2Fb%2F454752%2F1421818491377.jpg&h=24adc786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃蓉-2014版<br />\n小說黃蓉都係一等一靚女黎 而且足智多謀精靈 14年版似足中年貴婦 仲叫幾靚添<br />\n<img src=\"http://m3.biz.itc.cn/pic/new/n/70/07/Img7390770_n.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm3.biz.itc.cn%2Fpic%2Fnew%2Fn%2F70%2F07%2FImg7390770_n.JPG&h=8d13f0f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n06年版真係講都咪撚講 屌你老母 成個阿嬸咁<br />\n<img src=\"http://image2.sina.com.cn/ent/v/2005-05-10/U92P28T3D720106F326DT20050510192541.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage2.sina.com.cn%2Fent%2Fv%2F2005-05-10%2FU92P28T3D720106F326DT20050510192541.JPG&h=59dedc67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1995年既郭靖同黃蓉不提也罷<br />\n<br />\n東邪-無心水 無一個夠邪氣 (反而射鵰既黃秋生唔錯)<br />\n西毒-無心水<br />\n南僧-14版 夠慈祥<br />\n北丐-大SIR 其實佢個樣夠正義 睇落矮小 所以個FEEL好似<br />\n金輪-14版 其他都太過老 同埋金輪非大奸大惡之人 佢都係蒙古人 南下攻打大宋對佢係反而係正義之事 06版太過陰險<br />\n周伯通-14版同秦煌都好好 但14版就多幾分活潑 同表情變化做得好過秦煌<br />\n<br />\n程英-14年版 書中描述程英一個「柔」字 第一眼望落就覺得100% MATCH<br />\n陸無雙-14版同06版都好FEEL 夠晒「俏」<br />\n郭芙-14版 望落就知八婆格 加上算係靚<br />\n郭襄-無心水 好多人鍾意楊冪版 但我覺得楊冪得其活潑但無佢個情 硬係差少少咁<br />\n李莫愁-暫時14版 靚得黎有個似怨婿FEEL 特別係情花燒死個一幕 06版我屌你老母臭化閪<br />\n公孫綠萼-14版 無咁大陸FEEL<br />\n<br />\n總結 14版選角除左主角 其他都幾好 似係有心特登揀過黎 特別係程英揀得好好<br />\n但主角就揀名氣大既演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1792bba2594be804af7189c0265bc29825eb9054","tid":87820,"uid":46615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"楊過一定揀古仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dea7b2b75810c237f86932da890390bf370cef","tid":87820,"uid":27511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"06年完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35de63aea987e6248eb5539fa2e5656d87cc0ded","tid":87820,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:09:28.000Z","msg":"西毒一定係徐錦江<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51149730cec7fc325acc4602f7a097cf45546e85","tid":87820,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:15:35.000Z","msg":"東邪 秋生"},{"pid":"a3d7bd1960e772f966355df689075273588ac82b","tid":87820,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東邪 秋生</blockquote><br />\n呢句真 不過佢係射鵰度 唔係神鵰 所以無揀佢"},{"pid":"babb7dc6a79a5a032ba30bb41bbaea5c51cb77af","tid":87820,"uid":45335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:44:12.000Z","msg":"後生楊過應該係劉德華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c48a35e74b68ce905572c5ada65d5f58af45c1","tid":87820,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>06年完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n06年得2個主角揀得好<br />\n其他都totally shit啊"},{"pid":"7a649211eac33fe9841e8339c446314a9f2426a2","tid":87820,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"東邪 - 仆街二叔駱應鈞<br />\n北丐 - 叉燒炳<br />\n郭襄 - 李綺紅"},{"pid":"79497bb99fadb45363f6c4174cc0cb153ca68bf0","tid":87820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:26:04.000Z","msg":"14年郭靖邊忽有大俠feel <br />\n梁家仁就有"},{"pid":"239e6bc49cbffe5e86df4efcb55068ad72fb743f","tid":87820,"uid":68924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:27:32.000Z","msg":"劉亦菲做小龍女係沒得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377af30909915b35b5a05348c67d749f89147f4c","tid":87820,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:31:45.000Z","msg":"我仲諗緊邊個大陸仔叫無心水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n金庸話過劉小姐唔似小龍女"},{"pid":"aa8b7db1663a5de8cfad2fa6e7492138d561671d","tid":87820,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我仲諗緊邊個大陸仔叫無心水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW<br />\n金庸話過劉小姐唔似小龍女</blockquote><br />\nSOURCE?<br />\n單睇書 描述既小龍女同劉亦菲都好似啵 第一眼望落真正明白咩叫美若天仙"},{"pid":"adf47d3cab6b5930a61e8a8c30755acc44e5e2fb","tid":87820,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:16:41.000Z","msg":"14其實除左女主其他真係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9fb5196da28c3030d6062087788dd3f321c7ea","tid":87820,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683489819fbc8ceac793ccf0eb4bead7e8d8cf8c","tid":